    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. Since i'm trying to make a strong case for it in my paper, can u explain why some people say it's basically the only way to solve the housing crisis and make cities more livable? Like, what are the specific reasons why it's considered the best solution compared to other options?",
